#: ../../04_Data_presentation/Presentation_images.md:85
msgid "Lack of details and missing of key explanations will make it impossible for audiences to interpret image data in figures.  To unambiguously reference probes consider using terms from the ISAC Probe Tag Dictionary, a standardized nomenclature for probers used in cytometry and microscopy."
msgstr ""

